==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Japanese
<hw>Jap`a*nese"</hw>, <pos>n. sing. & pl.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A native or inhabitant of Japan; collectively, the
people of Japan.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <singf>sing.</singf> <def>The language of the people of
Japan, called in the Japanese language <xex>nihongo</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Japanned</ent>⟦br⟧
